ontent-assets/images/20231202_WBC544.png">他们的图表</a>显示我们的电动汽车销售仍在上升！ CNBC引用了有关经销商销售其电动汽车库存需要多长时间的数据，但是鉴于销售的增加，这只是经销商过于乐观和订购太多的标志。 Money.com 的文章将电动汽车销量与预期进行比较，而不是与上一年的实际销量进行比较。</p><p>当您查看实际数据时，很明显，到目前为止，实际上还没有放缓。美国人在 2023 年购买的电动汽车比 2022 年全年多了 20 万辆： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg" width="900" height="565" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/72bb6ce6-3dec-4244-a0c3-cd15e025a7c5_900x565.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&